<t font='PuristaBold'>Voluntary nature of study</t><br/>
Taking part in this study is voluntary. You may choose not to take part or may leave the study at any time. Leaving the study will not result in any penalty or loss of benefits to which you are entitled. Your decision whether or not to participate in this study will not affect your current or future relations with the researcher.<br/><br/>

